  <summary date="2021-10-21T14:40:02Z" status="Introduced in House">Prohibiting TSP Investment in China Act

This bill limits the investments of funds under the Thrift Savings Plan. Specifically, it prohibits funds, including funds that are accessible through a mutual fund window, from investing in any entity that is based in China or any subsidiary of such an entity.</summary>
